##Labels and position


```python
HumanPPI.nodes(data = 'name')
labels = dict(HumanPPI.nodes(data = 'symobl'))
labels
PPI = nx.relabel_nodes(HumanPPI, labels, copy=True)
print(PPI)
pos2 = nx.nx_agraph.graphviz_layout(PPI,prog='neato')
```
